[quote=“Cole1497, post:30, topic:425144”]I don’t use torrents, I just download a cracked .zip of programs. Like Cinema 4D. Or photoshop.[/quote]What’s the difference?

I find torrents easier because they run completely in the background, I can leave out unnecessary files and when starting my computer it automatically continues the downloading. My average download speed for torrents is 2MB/s and I limited my upload to 15kB/s because I don’t want to much traffic on my network.

Most of the time, you can also read comments and feedback to see if it is a legitimate torrent.
